 an election & let them prove he's still alive.", "last_comment_created": 1784679300077, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 26, "score_up": 536, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "Kentucky Gov. Andy Beshear said two unidentified agencies told him that Sen. Mitch McConnell (R-KY) had died while the senator was hospitalized, but the Democrat governor has refused to identify the callers or explain what he did with the information.", "large_image": "Xvp7nRPrGMWALyvb.png", "title": "Kentucky Governor Says Two Agencies Told Him Mitch McConnell Died in Hospital - Slay News"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBzwtenm", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 31, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8740946, "raw_content": "", "author": "TheRedPilledArtist", "created": 1784685888404, "profile_picture": "gLOjTx59Rfh7", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Covidrrhea", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBzwtenm.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/zt0AvLNmfeaJ.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/kehu3jVMnPTAozDA.png", "width": 768, "content-type": "png", "height": 305}], "blurhash": "UA7w$ynO%2%2~WR5-p%2sAMx-pxHs:V@xuoL", "full_resolution": [347, 873]}, "title": "\ud83d\udc7d \ud835\udc00\ud835\udc27\ud835\udc1d \ud835\udc12\ud835\udc28 \ud835\udc08\ud835\udc2d \ud835\udc01\ud835\udc1e\ud835\udc20\ud835\udc22\ud835\udc27\ud835\udc2c: President Trump has directed federal agencies to WAIVE prior NDAs for former officials and contractors who wish to share UAP (UFO) information with designated government investigators...", "last_comment_created": 1784690161995, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 4, "score_up": 31, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBzwsHtE", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 76, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8740494, "raw_content": "\u201cTwo weeks ago, someone in your circle made sure to leak the sharp conversation you had with Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu. And I deliberately emphasize the full title. He is not \u2018Bibi.\u2019 He is the elected prime minister of the independent and sovereign State of Israel, as would be anyone else sitting in his chair.\u201d\n\n\u201cAnd I am trying, and failing, to understand what caused this absurd change of direction, so contrary to everything you have said and done until now. The midterm elections are a flimsy excuse. You are in your second term, and the surrender memorandum of understanding will hurt the Republicans more than it will help them.\u201d\n\n\"One last word... We feel betrayed, nothing less, because your heart was, it seemed, in the right place, with all your flaws. You acted against it. You lost your patience and your moral and leadership compass. O\u0274\u029f\u028f \u026a\ua730 \u028f\u1d0f\u1d1c \u1d21\u1d00\u029f\u1d0b \u1d1b\u029c\u026as \u0299\u1d00\u1d04\u1d0b \u1d00\u0274\u1d05 \u1d00\u1d20\u1d0f\u026a\u1d05 \u0280\u1d07\u1d00\u1d04\u029c\u026a\u0274\u0262 \u1d00 \ua730\u026a\u0274\u1d00\u029f \u1d00\u0262\u0280\u1d07\u1d07\u1d0d\u1d07\u0274\u1d1b \u1d21\u026a\u1d1b\u029c I\u0280\u1d00\u0274 \u1d0d\u026a\u0262\u029c\u1d1b \u1d1b\u029c\u1d07\u0280\u1d07 \u0299\u1d07 \u1d00 \u1d04\u1d0f\u0280\u0280\u1d07\u1d04\u1d1b\u026a\u1d0f\u0274.\"\n\nhttps://vinnews.com/2026/06/20/israeli-newspaper-owned-by-miriam-adelson-slams-trumps-betrayal-and-colossal-mistake/", "author": "Lunar", "created": 1784668187784, "profile_picture": "AAVSlrgdPsSU", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "anotherthing", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Israel's largest newspaper-- owned by AIPAC mega-donor Miriam Adelson-- has turned on President Trump, addressing him directly with these vicious words:", "last_comment_created": 1784688067336, "content": "<p>\u201cTwo weeks ago, someone in your circle made sure to leak the sharp conversation you had with Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu. And I deliberately emphasize the full title. He is not \u2018Bibi.\u2019 He is the elected prime minister of the independent and sovereign State of Israel, as would be anyone else sitting in his chair.\u201d</p>\n<p>\u201cAnd I am trying, and failing, to understand what caused this absurd change of direction, so contrary to everything you have said and done until now. The midterm elections are a flimsy excuse. You are in your second term, and the surrender memorandum of understanding will hurt the Republicans more than it will help them.\u201d</p>\n<p>&quot;One last word... We feel betrayed, nothing less, because your heart was, it seemed, in the right place, with all your flaws. You acted against it. You lost your patience and your moral and leadership compass. O\u0274\u029f\u028f \u026a\ua730 \u028f\u1d0f\u1d1c \u1d21\u1d00\u029f\u1d0b \u1d1b\u029c\u026as \u0299\u1d00\u1d04\u1d0b \u1d00\u0274\u1d05 \u1d00\u1d20\u1d0f\u026a